-- Toyota August U.S. auto sales down 9.4 percent
-- 
-- Wed Sep 3, 2008 1:03pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/03/businesspro-usa-autosales-toyota-dc-idUSWNAB926920080903

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Toyota Motor Corp ( 7203.T )( TM.N ) said 
on Wednesday its U.S. auto sales fell 9.4 percent in August, 
led by a 16.4 percent drop in truck sales. 

  Sales declined to 211,533 vehicles in August from 233,471 
vehicles a year earlier, Toyota said.  Toyota brand sales fell 9.4 percent, while sales were down 
9.1 percent in its luxury Lexus brand.  (Reporting by  Soyoung Kim ; editing by Jeffrey Benkoe)